Content: Are you someone who focuses solely on technical expertise when it comes to hiring or building a career? It's time to rethink that approach. While technical skills are undoubtedly important, soft skills are equally crucial for success in today's rapidly changing world.

Name: Khushboo Verma
Content: Most companies have behavioural rounds as a part of their hiring process and evaluate candidates on the above mentioned skills. Often candidates take these rounds lightly, but to a company or startup that values its culture, this round can often become a decision making factor.

Name: Khushboo Verma
Content: So if you're looking to build a successful career or grow your business, don't overlook the importance of soft skills. Invest in developing your emotional intelligence, communication, teamwork, and other soft skills, and you'll be well on your way to success.
